!TITLE
ILLUMINED BY HIS LOVE
!WORDS
The older we become, the deeper the lines of holiness should be 
etched upon our countenance! Someone has well said, "Every man is 
responsible for his face at 50.  Those who walk with Jesus should 
mirror His character by their happy and serene appearance!"

     A dear old saint had "permanent waves" in his face.  That is to 
say, he looked so long upon life with a smile and with an attitude of 
tranquillity and good will, that those lines were fixed in his 
expression.  His face had set into an abiding vision of love and 
contentment.  It's the kind of "beauty treatment" the Lord gives to 
His long-time friends!
