!TITLE
A GOD LIKE ME
!WORDS
In Kyoto, Japan, is an unusual place of worship called "The Temple of 
the Thousand Buddhas."  On display inside the shrine are more than a 
thousand likenesses of Buddha, each just a little different from the 
others.  They are there so the devotee can come in, find the one that 
looks the most like himself, and worship it.  How sad!  Yet, how much 
like people the world over.
