!TITLE
HOW MANY IS A BILLION?
!WORDS
Statistics show that only four percent of Christian giving goes to 
missions involving non- English-speaking people.  Since 91 percent of 
the earth's nearly 4 billion inhabitants fall into that category, it 
is estimated that over half of the world has never heard the Gospel 
once!

     Do you have any idea just how many units it takes to make a 
billion!  All the minutes contained in 1800 years still would not 
reach that total.  When we think of this enormous figure, we are 
staggered by the number of workers that must be recruited to reach 
the masses who have never been confronted with the message of 
salvation.
