!TITLE
PEOPLE OF COURAGE
!WORDS
One day an unarmed housewife captured three burglars singlehandedly.  
When the woman returned home after picking up her daughter from 
school, three men were loading household items into their car parked 
in her driveway.  She pulled her van behind their car.  Then she 
ordered the men to carry her belongings back into the house and sit 
on the couch until the police arrived.  Later, when asked why they 
didn't escape, she replied, "The good Lord was with me.  I was kind 
and considerate.  Besides, I wasn't going to move my van so they 
could get away."

  It's not so easy to know when such boldness is wise or foolhardy.  
Only the Holy Spirit can show us.  But one thing is sure, Christians 
have reason to be the most courageous people on earth.
!TOPICS
