!TITLE
IT'S COMING
!WORDS
 David Bryant of Concerts of Prayer International tells of taking a 
stroll along the beach with his family.  Just a mile inland from 
where they were walking was a large airport.  As the children played 
in the sand, David noticed that there was an airplane quite a ways 
out over the water.  It seemed to be just hanging there over the 
horizon. He could see its landing lights so he knew it was headed 
toward the airport, but it didn't seem to be moving at all.

   After a few minutes the "stationary" airplane began to rumble and 
David could see it getting bigger.  When it roared over his head, he 
finally got a better picture of the incredible speed and power at 
which it had been coming directly toward him all along.  How could he 
have ever thought it was standing still?

   David sees this as an apt picture of what's happening in North 
America today.  For several years now, the hope for spiritual 
awakening has been like a dot on the horizon, but now as the prayer 
movement gathers momentum it's "as if we can hear the roar of the 
engines as the jet looms larger."  Revival is at hand!

   [Evangelical Advocate, Jul 1996.  Pages 7-8.]
!TOPICS
